{"tid":1298301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請廣傳！促請社聯終止災後心理輔導協會會籍聯署聲明","createTime":"2019-07-09T00:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T07:13:48.000Z","uid":212944,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0bf9127b0d40b860823af3584b2f7ca0147de02","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:03:10.000Z","msg":"杜永政自創資歷就走出來呃人<br />\n根本就唔係專業輔導人員，連PTSD都誤診<br />\n仲要拎來賺錢！<br />\n希望大家幫手聯署，雖然未必推到佢仆街，但至少少個資歷先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfq7LhArNExPQe06-Gi1eO7ajxnGv7aVqzxYIOvErI9rPRvRQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfq7LhArNExPQe06-Gi1eO7ajxnGv7aVqzxYIOvErI9rPRvRQ%2Fviewform&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=5a28ff15\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfq7LhArNExPQe06-Gi1eO7ajxnGv7aVqzxYIOvErI9rPRvRQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n促請香港社會服務聯會（社聯）終止災後心理輔導協會會籍聯署聲明<br />\n<br />\n近日連串的社會事件使不少市民的情緒受到困擾，一個名為「災後心理輔導協會」（PCCN）的機構設立「救心熱線」，呼籲市民向該機構求助。然而，有媒體於2019年7月5日的報導發現，該機構背景、輔導及治療過程問題重重，包括：<br />\n<br />\n一、輔導員誤診創傷後壓力症，令求助者更崩潰；<br />\n二、該機構實習輔導員為求助者進行眼動療法，事前無問臨床病史，被香港心理學會註冊臨床心理學家指做法危險；<br />\n三、該機構總幹事杜永政並非臨床心理學家亦無眼動療法培訓師資格，但自己成立學會認證自己培訓的輔導員，學員的認可資格成疑；<br />\n四、<a href=\"http://該機構聲稱自己是國際救援組織協調資訊平台MHPSS.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A9%B2%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0MHPSS.net&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=bbace650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">該機構聲稱自己是國際救援組織協調資訊平台MHPSS.net</a>及Humanitarian Response會員，但Humanitarian Response根本不設會員制，<a href=\"http://而MHPSS.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%80%8CMHPSS.net&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=c23372fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">而MHPSS.net</a>的個人會員是任何人都可免費申請，該機構聲稱自己是「聯合國組織」會員，有嚴重誤導市民之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，早與2015年5月已有媒體發現PCCN總幹事杜永政訛稱自己為「白宮認可專家」，機構的輔導及「救援工作」亦存在不當做法，惟近日多個主流媒體依然頻頻採訪杜永政，若如其聲稱已有超過200個個案向PCCN求助的話，求助者的情況確實令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n基於上述原因，我們認為災後心理輔導協會的操守及行為嚴重損害社聯聲譽。因此發起不同專業及公眾聯署，促請社聯執行委員會按照 貴會指引立即終止災後心理輔導協會會籍，以保社聯聲譽，亦藉此舉向市民說明該機構的認受性及專業資格成疑，及應避免向該機構尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n一群關注心理健康的市民、教育工作者、香港心理學會註冊心理學家、註冊社工、傳媒工作者、醫生及護士 (排列以首字筆劃序)"},{"pid":"0fedb5eed1b6e3409a9932ecffb0822dad3e2ac7","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0db90653e19f06cb909e48d23e1083e8de6ece3f","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:05:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bde4e4d4ff5db5177aa857d1a7a4b893bf06d59c","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7df4e9ac965c3f2ca82346b19d22b9053b97cfb9","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:05:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3150b8b99223450b47a4450f02b3f814fd105c06","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b03ae9a4cc2d30e98fe39bc1b65cd02f3dc3091a","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dca07b52f6e32fc5f4c9435173cd704aa8713c0","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:07:22.000Z","msg":"提提大家，佢地有講明如果求助人有透露違法行為，佢地係會同警方聯絡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a79382636de5210ff1f376f2aeac338cc9fdb3","tid":1298301,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:08:08.000Z","msg":"港共成功左 由得我地和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n你地開始玩膠，即係證明你地不再憤怒，覺得好開心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298176</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9dc1c0f24167e4c410aa9d636877a2240e0f72f3","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:10:53.000Z","msg":"[推爆佢] 小心呢條救心熱線！！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240471\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[ 大踢爆 ] 唔好再搵呢條救心熱線! 一齊推爆佢!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1290951\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1290951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[幫手推爆佢] 有需要 搵人輔導唔緊要 但要小心紅底救心熱線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1287755\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1287755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"605b12c23fb29bd89d7f123dd53d092ed774c518","tid":1298301,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:11:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"244e9baa0e21a30e4e37c531e5f0ce09f6bfef15","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f55a02238f205f4a5ded8b24a9bb4ad6e15a3f8e","tid":1298301,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98295432d539e7f18bc6f501db0f7b91ca8104da","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:17:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55904a196e967cfa2a4effc6e29cbc7a7889fd3b","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"252c87295a38dd32d97f8357edad8a1da19dfa03","tid":1298301,"uid":226716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:00:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e68611eecc7461ce335c372984c2dfc8b65b515f","tid":1298301,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1796c29d42de3df906b24226a7509f7ae4c08f81","tid":1298301,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"重申7大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷對抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 追究黑警暴行，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 落實真雙普選<br />\n6. 承諾不推行社會信用評分制度<br />\n7. 拆除所有監控燈柱"}]}